{"tid":422860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有睇使徒行者2既入一入黎","createTime":"2017-10-03T12:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T10:07:55.000Z","uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4379d8a395606694d601d2cda4020b020097666d","tid":422860,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"宣萱係前英國臥底<br />\n<br />\n袁偉豪係臥底<br />\n<br />\n麥明詩係臥底<br />\n<br />\n麥明詩條仔後來變左黑警<br />\n<br />\n炮仗死左<br />\n<br />\n飛機哥比周柏豪踢死左<br />\n<br />\n暫時係得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實套野上網已經有得睇1-20集 仲係粵語 <br />\n<br />\n所以鍾意睇既巴打唔好再on99咁每晚等睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24970852505f583462d4e84895319d215a5d907a","tid":422860,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70bd290662245ba05d0285423ba80df30e2e7bf9","tid":422860,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:11:34.000Z","msg":"有無網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8593d3e381f9c6235888dd51f7aa4a2f0fc2066a","tid":422860,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:14:14.000Z","msg":"等緊出21，殺完白先生"},{"pid":"241cb12d619754f947c9eae77cfdfd8893fa911d","tid":422860,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"又係好人受壓逼 啲壞人臨尾忽然間戇鳩犯個低級錯誤要坐監收皮嘅垃圾劇<br />\n<br />\n等香港人覺得香港有公義 繼續受壓逼 有暇想 以為班仆街會被天收 以為殺人放火唔會有金腰帶  唔可以濫用私刑 要等個官判<br />\n<br />\n仆街電視台來來去去律師警察"},{"pid":"6e782e37c5d433edb947f4c460414ba573118cda","tid":422860,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"飛住睇5集，用左3個鐘<br />\n五晚睇5集，用5個鐘<br />\n人生慳左2個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d405a563e634a043be5750e78fbf09308d7b4fc","tid":422860,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":